get those 2 PM hanger shakes.

00:23:17.930 --> 00:23:19.530
Sad, stressed, tired, bored--

00:23:19.530 --> 00:23:21.074
or hangry-- and bored.

00:23:21.074 --> 00:23:22.740
If you're bored,
again, that's something

00:23:22.740 --> 00:23:27.360
that your brain actually needs
energy when you're bored.

00:23:27.360 --> 00:23:30.300
And so if you're a bored
eater, where you're just like,

00:23:30.300 --> 00:23:32.549
oh, I have nothing else
to do, chips sound great.

00:23:32.549 --> 00:23:34.840
And then you're like, well,
now I need something sweet.

00:23:34.840 --> 00:23:36.150
So this sounds great.

00:23:36.150 --> 00:23:37.920
