listening to your body,

00:23:52.470 --> 00:23:55.140
feeling your feelings,
prescribing food as necessary--

00:23:55.140 --> 00:23:57.600
all of these things are
this really intricate dance

00:23:57.600 --> 00:24:02.230
that your body will work with
you on, if you choose to listen

00:24:02.230 --> 00:24:05.970
and if you choose to really
understand the deeper

00:24:05.970 --> 00:24:09.810
connections that the food
and mood plays into it.

00:24:09.810 --> 00:24:20.430
