and to wrap all this together,

00:24:20.430 --> 00:24:23.370
I want to read a quick
little thing from my book.

00:24:23.370 --> 00:24:28.500
It's called the "Food
Mood Girl Femifesto."

00:24:28.500 --> 00:24:30.000
And this kind of
wraps up everything

00:24:30.000 --> 00:24:33.170
that we just talked about.

00:24:33.170 --> 00:24:35.870
Your body is a magical machine.

00:24:35.870 --> 00:24:38.690
It's like a computer
program specifically for you

00:24:38.690 --> 00:24:40.340
and only you.

00:24:40.340 --> 00:24:41.450
Cherish it.

00:24:41.450 --> 00:24:42.560
Trust it.

00:24:42.560 --> 00:24:44.259
Treat it with respect.

00:24:44.259 --> 00:24:45.800
Talk to your body
like you would talk

00:24:45.800 --> 00:24:48.380
to a really cute dog,
except not in public,

00:24:48.380 --> 00:24:50.720
because that might be weird.

00:24:50.720 --> 00:24:53.600
Take time to eat
really good real food.

00:24:53.600 --> 00:24:57.080
That includes leafy
greens and a cookie.

00:24:57.080 --> 00:24:58.580
Eat everything with love.

00:24:58.580 --> 00:25:00.080
Cook everything with love.

00:25:00.080 --> 00:25:03.500
Love is always the
secret ingredient.

00:25:03.500 --> 00:25:04.880
Ask questions.

00:25:04.880 --> 00:25:06.530
Be open to growth.

00:25:06.530 --> 00:25:08.150
Ask more questions.

00:25:08.150 --> 00:25:10.910
Be kind to yourself and others.

00:25:10.910 --> 00:25:12.350
Release judgments.

00:25:12.350 --> 00:25:14.390
Challenge conventional norms.

00:25:14.390 --> 00:25:16.610
Do something that scares you.

00:25:16.610 --> 00:25:19.220
Listen more, react less.

00:25:19.220 --> 00:25:22.490
Laugh your ass off, preferably
in the company of others,

00:25:22.490 --> 00:25:25.530
but by yourself is cool too.

00:25:25.530 --> 00:25:26.940
Listen to your gut.

00:25:26.940 --> 00:25:28.710
Always listen to your gut.

00:25:28.710 --> 00:25:31.530
It's right 99% of the time.

00:25:31.530 --> 00:25:33.960
Embrace your body's unique size.

00:25:33.960 --> 00:25:36.480
Know that it will
change and evolve.

00:25:36.480 --> 00:25:40.920
It might grow and shrink, but
it still loves you all the same.

00:25:40.920 --> 00:25:42.690
And above all, love yourself.

00:25:42.690 --> 00:25:44.910
Like, really, truly
love yourself.

00:25:44.910 --> 00:25:47.610
Celebrate and appreciate
yourself daily.

00:25:47.610 --> 00:25:50.490
And remember, this is the
only body in life you have.

00:25:50.490 --> 00:25:53.750
So love it up the best you can.

